snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Terry Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Terry from Fatal Fury will show he’s bark, bite, and rising fang when he scores a slam dunk in Street Fighter 6 on September 24!

With seven special moves, unique target combos, and resourceful Super Arts at his disposal, Terry is a powerful wave to be reckoned with.

Terry can be purchased individually with Fighter Coins and the owners of the Year 2 Character Pass / Ultimate Pass will automatically get access to Terry when he releases.

https://streetfighter.com/6/

©CAPCOM ©SNK
